query:
UPDATE flavors
        SET
            arch = $2::text::arch,
            brand = $3,
            model = $4,
            cpu_count = $5,
            description = $6,
            cpu_frequency_mhz = $7,
            cpu_model = $8,
            ram_bytes = $9,
            root_size_bytes = $10,
            disk_size_bytes = $11,
            storage_type = $12::text::storage_type,
            network_speed_mbps = $13,
            network_interfaces = $14,
            deleted = false
        WHERE name = $1;
